Class DataNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • za.ac.wits.elen4010.fluidsim.gui.DataNode

  • public class DataNode
extends java.lang.Object
    The data node acts as the lowest level of the heirarchy for the TimeCapture class. It has a name and the CSV data stored as a string
    See Also:
